OL,3,CCareless driver sentenced after near
OL,4,Cserious collision in Warwick
OL,6,FA careless driver has been sentenced
OL,7,Fafter nearly causing a serious
OL,8,Fcollision in Warwick.
OL,10,FThe 25-year-old from Coventry
OL,11,Fattempted to overtake a van, clipping
OL,12,Fit in the process and leaving debris
OL,13,Fscattered across Silver Eagle Way in
OL,14,FBaginton in April last year.
OL,16,FDashcam footage showed they also
OL,17,Fnarrowly missed a collision with an
OL,18,FHGV travelling in the opposite
OL,19,Fdirection.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
