FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772903477
OL,3,CCareless driver sentenced after near
OL,4,Cserious collision in Warwick
OL,6,FDespite damaging the van, he failed to
OL,7,Fstop or report the incident to the
OL,8,Fpolice.
OL,10,FThe van driver had captured the entire
OL,11,Fincident on his dashcam. He submitted
OL,12,Fthe footage to the police, where it
OL,13,Fwas reviewed and he was sent a Notice
OL,14,Fof Intended Prosecution (NIP).
OL,16,FAfter pleading guilty in court, he was
OL,17,Fdisqualified from driving for six
OL,18,Fmonths, handed a Community Order,
OL,19,Frequiring him to complete 120 hours of
OL,20,Funpaid supervised work, and ordered to
OL,21,Fpay #250 in costs and victim surcharge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
