PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1772903477
OL,3,CCareless driver sentenced after near
OL,4,Cserious collision in Warwick
OL,6,FMrs Smith, Police Led Prosecutor said:
OL,7,F"This collision shows how valuable
OL,8,Fdashcam can be as the footage provided
OL,9,Fclear evidence of what had happened.
OL,10,FThe other driver stated he could find
OL,11,Fno damage to his car, but the footage
OL,12,Fclearly shows the damage sustained and
OL,13,Fwe were able to use this as evidence
OL,14,Fin court.
OL,16,F"We can only hope the sixmonth
OL,17,Fdriving ban and unpaid work serves as
OL,18,Fa wakeup call and encourages him to
OL,19,Fthink more carefully about how he
OL,20,Fdrives in future."
